flowchart TD
    A[Start] --> B{Two date arguments?}
    B -- No --> C[Print usage and exit]
    B -- Yes --> D[Parse first date]
    D --> E{First date valid?}
    E -- No --> C
    E -- Yes --> F[Strip leading zeros]
    F --> G[Convert first date to day index]
    G --> H[Parse second date]
    H --> I{Second date valid?}
    I -- No --> C
    I -- Yes --> J[Strip leading zeros]
    J --> K[Convert second date to day index]
    K --> L[Subtract indexes]
    L --> M[Take absolute value]
    M --> N[Print day difference]
    N --> O[Exit]
